OL,3,CRob Burrow: What is motor neurone
OL,4,Cdisease?
OL,6,FRugby league legend Rob Burrow was one
OL,7,Fof several players diagnosed with
OL,8,Fmotor neurone disease (MND) in recent
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,F, was aged 37 and had three children
OL,12,Funder the age of eight with wife
OL,13,FLindsey when he announced in December
OL,14,F2019 that he had the degenerative
OL,15,Fdisease.
OL,17,FHere are some key questions and
OL,18,Fanswers about MND:
OL,20,FWhat is MND?
