OL,3,CRob Burrow: What is motor neurone
OL,4,Cdisease?
OL,6,FHow is MND treated and can it be cured?
OL,8,FThere is no cure for MND and the
OL,9,Fdisease will progress over time,
OL,10,Faccording to the MND Association.
OL,12,FHow long people live with the
OL,13,Fcondition varies, but some survive for
OL,14,Fyears, and even decades. Professor
OL,15,FStephen Hawking lived for more than 50
OL,16,Fyears after being diagnosed at the age
OL,17,Fof 21.
