OL,3,CRob Burrow: What is motor neurone
OL,4,Cdisease?
OL,6,FMND can be treated with occupational
OL,7,Ftherapy, physiotherapy, a medicine
OL,8,Fcalled riluzole and medication to
OL,9,Frelieve muscle stiffness and help with
OL,10,Fsaliva problems, the NHS said.
OL,12,FWho does the condition affect?
OL,14,FAccording to the MND Association, up
OL,15,Fto 5,000 adults in the UK have the
OL,16,Fdisease at any one time.
OL,18,FThe organisation says it can affect
OL,19,Fany adult at any age, but it is more
OL,20,Flikely to occur in people over the age
OL,21,Fof 50.
