OL,3,CRob Burrow: What is motor neurone
OL,4,Cdisease?
OL,6,FAre rugby players more at risk of MND?
OL,8,FIn 2022, a study led by the University
OL,9,Fof Glasgow found evidence of a
OL,10,Fconsiderably increased risk of the
OL,11,Fdegenerative disease among former
OL,12,Frugby players.
OL,14,FThe research, published in the Journal
OL,15,Fof Neurology Neurosurgery &
OL,16,FPsychiatry, compared health outcomes
OL,17,Famong 412 male former internationals
OL,18,Fand more than 1,200 matched
OL,19,Findividuals from the general
OL,20,Fpopulation.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/9
