OL,3,CRob Burrow: What is motor neurone
OL,4,Cdisease?
OL,6,FIt found that ex-rugby players had
OL,7,Fmore than twice the risk of a
OL,8,Fneurodegenerative disease, and a 15
OL,9,Ftimes higher risk of an MND diagnosis.
OL,11,FThe study prompted calls for the
OL,12,Felimination of contact training and a
OL,13,Freduction in the global rugby calendar.
OL,15,FWhich rugby players have been
OL,16,Fdiagnosed with the disease?
OL,18,FGloucester lock Ed Slater announced in
OL,19,F2022 that he would be retiring at the
OL,20,Fage of 34 after being diagnosed with
OL,21,FMND.
